---
title: "Sequence Diagram (Analysis) - Add a Worker"
config:
  theme: neutral
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant B as WorkerFormScreen<br>«boundary»
    participant C as AddWorkerController<br>«control»
    participant E as Worker<br>«entity»

    User->>B: select option 1, enter worker info
    B->>C: worker data
    C->>C: validate (code, age, salary)
    alt data valid
        C->>E: create and store Worker
        C-->>B: success
        B-->>User: "Add worker successfully!"
    else data invalid
        C-->>B: error message
        B-->>User: show localized error
    end
